                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Once (if) &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4611&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4611&lt;/a&gt; lands, a directory with custom style elements will be available to enhance the design of the Manual.&lt;/p&gt;

